Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:11.40,SignD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fr15\fs66\bord0\pos(640,232)\blur2\bord0\shad0\c&H897E84&}Trimite?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ce?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ce se întâmplă?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poftim, Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ce se petrece aici?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ce vrei să spui?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oamenii... De ce au dispărut toți oamenii?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Au dispărut?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Au dispărut toți!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toți oamenii de aici! Chiar în fața noastră!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nu știu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nu știi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ai văzut și tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nu? Nu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eu nu am...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ce tot spui...
