Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:52.88,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Zeci de miliarde de inimi care bat
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:59.84,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}anata ni wa matataki teido no saji na toukyuu
Dialogue: 2,0:10:52.88,0:10:59.84,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Pentru tine sunt doar o clipire, un scurt r{\fnCentury Gothic}ă{\fn}gaz.
