Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:04.89,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Chiar dac{\fnCentury Gothic}ă{\fn} te fr{\fnCentury Gothic}ă{\fn}mân{\fnCentury Gothic}ț{\fn}i cu gândul la viitor, cufundat înc{\fnCentury Gothic}ă{\fn} în trecut,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:10.77,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}chiri hitotsu gosan wo yurusanu hitsuzen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:10.77,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Nici m{\fnCentury Gothic}ă{\fn}car un fir de praf nu va fi iertat de inevitabilul calcul al erorii.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:16.98,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}mugen ni hirogaru yume mo egaku mirai mo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:16.98,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Visul care se extinde la {\fnCentury Gothic}„{\fn}infinit{\fnCentury Gothic}” ș{\fn}i viitorul pe care îl contur{\fnCentury Gothic}ă{\fn}m
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:22.86,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}bokutachi ni yurusareta kyoei no genri
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:22.86,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sunt drepturile iluzorii care ni s-au îng{\fnCentury Gothic}ă{\fn}duit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:28.87,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,250)}yuugen sore wa futatsu no hari ga shimesu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:28.87,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,250)}{\fnCentury Gothic}„{\fn}Finit{\fnCentury Gothic}”{\fn} – acesta este semnul celor dou{\fnCentury Gothic}ă{\fn} ace
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:33.62,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(250,0)}zankoku na yakujou to sentaku e
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:33.62,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(250,0)}Pentru un pact crud {\fnCentury Gothic}ș{\fn}i o alegere.
