Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Primit pe 23 iulie, ora 12:56...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:36.94,Cellphone,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(880,447)\blur2}Makise Kuris
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:37.56,Cellphone,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(880,447)\blur2}u a fost înj
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:38.02,Cellphone,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(880,447)\blur2}unghiată...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vezi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Săptămâna trecută... Stai să verific la mine.
