Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:44.78,CellphoneL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}\NDaru \NSă mergem! \N\N\N\N\NMayuri \NUită-te la asta\N\N\N\N\NMayuri \NRe: Nu-l vinde
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dispărut!
